<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3703011>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Luctithonus Lingafelter, new genus. a) Head, anterior view. b) Antennal scape. c) Elytron showing location of basal crest. d) Hind tibia and tarsus. e) Anterior view of elytra showing location and extent of tufts. f) Prosternum and mesosternum. g) Pronotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3703011/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

